score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U727o8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU727o8p.jpg&h=6c0aa0fc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8c81f927677f8f46953a4c7c73691e36ea375e","tid":198180,"uid":26110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U727o8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU727o8p.jpg&h=6c0aa0fc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a4e379f8ad76347aea49464e5f3676b6d4ef9c","tid":198180,"uid":9644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"如果係樓上滲水要叫樓上搞咗先 佢唔搞點整都冇用 到時成塊石屎飛落去你頭就大濟 呢啲係佢地責任來 唔整可以出信<br />\n<br />\n但首先你摸下牆係未涼涼地 濕濕地先 如果係你就要同樓上講聲"},{"pid":"7e692e5fbed462658be347d428718be21d23316a","tid":198180,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:58:21.000Z","msg":"剷曬佢，用防霉漆，或者試下響油漆度加漂白水<br />\n但都唔治本<br />\n最緊要裝個浴室寶，<br />\n日日係咁抽濕"},{"pid":"5e8de7c0828c5125c1df513c1317271ba5b8ad16","tid":198180,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0da33158fbcd1c128dee4d2f9c08c023e0cf75a9","tid":198180,"uid":54439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用漂白水抹吓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a502c9f4ec983fde5b2748b496824b0da79268","tid":198180,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U727o8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU727o8p.jpg&h=6c0aa0fc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該係講油黑哂佢，以後就一了百了"},{"pid":"ad52d9dd416f140eb3ec0b5f9210732cfc33b4f1","tid":198180,"uid":54439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U727o8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU727o8p.jpg&h=6c0aa0fc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該係講油黑哂佢，以後就一了百了</blockquote><br />\n摸黑沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4905307dd77ba593d77606d6e3645e4ee645989","tid":198180,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好近山邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有個市區公園係隔離，算唔算山?"},{"pid":"170db936a79d5dab08a24f70fd9fb8f493dfe4d3","tid":198180,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剷曬佢，用防霉漆，或者試下響油漆度加漂白水<br />\n但都唔治本<br />\n最緊要裝個浴室寶，<br />\n日日係咁抽濕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用柒鏟鏟定用沙紙磨?<br />\n<br />\n濕呢樣真，廁所無對流風，成日都好濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a42e32377e79b8fe0204405c3a76866b95c172","tid":198180,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用漂白水抹吓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抹一次d灰實甩撚哂落黎"},{"pid":"7fea028c3d61edc7a5d0a321f61e8c8bb15e0cf1","tid":198180,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵人人（搬屋公司）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搬個廁所去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a80f1043bbb89c7325c5f2429297ea45c63d95","tid":198180,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有可能係樓上滲水？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔似係滲水，無乜水印<br />\n<br />\n其實好多年架啦，不過無時間理，每年回<br />\n<br />\n南天更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋廁所長期都比較濕，無陽光入廁所"},{"pid":"6dc39d4180ba499330aeddc9e70a399b403473bb","tid":198180,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"整個假天花算啦"}]}